Title: Chapter 7 Artistic Design with GA NN  
Author: Henrik Hautop Lund, Luigi Pagliarini, Orazio Miglino 
Keyword: Artistic Design, Neural Networks, Artificial Life, Aesthetic Evaluation, Evolvable Mathematical Formulae.  
Note: The complete title of this article: Artistic Design with Genetic Algorithms and Neural Networks. This is a b/w version of the original colour version, why the images do not appear in the correct form as constructed by AP. 97  
